prod.desciption:
Jordan Brand offers a fresh take on the Jordan 1 Mid silhouette with the Air Jordan 1 Mid Triple White 2.

The Air Jordan 1 Mid Triple White 2 features an ultra-clean white leather-look throughout, giving the design a luxury look. The signature Jumpman logo and Jordan's Wings logo are featured on the tongue and collar, respectively. At the bottom of the sneaker, a white sole completes the design.

The Air Jordan Mid Triple White 2 released in June of 2020 and retailed for $115.
